{"id":3179,"title":"The management of abnormal haemostasis in the ICU.","abstract":"The aetiology and management of haemostatic abnormalities in critical care patients are considered in this narrative review. The mechanisms of normal haemostasis and derangements that occur as a result of sepsis and organ dysfunction are discussed. Finally, the management of haemostatic abnormalities as they relate to critical care practice are considered, including the management of heparin-induced thrombocytopenia. ","date":"2014-12-02","categories":"Hemic and Lymphatic Diseases","split":"test","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25440406","annotations":[{"name":"Sepsis","weight":0.488317,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sepsis"},{"name":"Etiology","weight":0.384722,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Etiology"},{"name":"Intensive-care medicine","weight":0.114801,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intensive-care_medicine"},{"name":"Intensive care unit","weight":0.0539958,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Intensive_care_unit"},{"name":"Hemostasis","weight":0.0342852,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hemostasis"},{"name":"Antihemorrhagic","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antihemorrhagic"},{"name":"Thrombocytopenia","weight":0.0287296,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thrombocytopenia"},{"name":"Management","weight":0.0276227,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Management"},{"name":"Multiple organ dysfunction syndrome","weight":0.0224886,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multiple_organ_dysfunction_syndrome"},{"name":"Derangement","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Derangement"},{"name":"Organ (anatomy)","weight":0.0152478,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Organ_(anatomy)"},{"name":"Mental disorder","weight":0.0147415,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mental